         NC_TRAD_CEQ(nco2,i,a,r)$ total("new",r) = (NC_TRAD_CEQ(nco2,i,a,r) * total("old",r)/total("new",r)) $ (vdfb(i,a,r) + vmfb(i,a,r)) ;

